{
  "id": "6a35bf31cf9a39fa2bec1801",
  "title": "共武装化",
  "created": 1781907271,
  "updated": 1781907756,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a35bf31cf9a39fa2bec1801",
      "text": "共武装化",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781907271,
      "updated": 1781907271
    },
    {
      "id": "6a35bf1c00000000003e791d",
      "text": " [ジパング政策]の目玉（五大政策、五化け）の一つ[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781907271,
      "updated": 1781907323
    },
    {
      "id": "6a35bfcc00000000003e7920",
      "text": "  英：commilitarization",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781907448,
      "updated": 1781907454
    },
    {
      "id": "6a35bf1d00000000003e791e",
      "text": "  国の規模にかかわらず全主権国家が対等に軍事力を持てる軍事同盟「共武装同盟」を作り拡大していく[安全保障]政策",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781907272,
      "updated": 1781907493
    },
    {
      "id": "6a35c08900000000003e7923",
      "text": "   「主権国家の自立のための軍事力」を保証する",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781907637,
      "updated": 1781907744
    },
    {
      "id": "6a35bf5100000000003e791f",
      "text": "   この過程を「共軍拡」と呼ぶ",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781907324,
      "updated": 1781907575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a35c02400000000003e7922",
      "text": "  外部に脅威がなくなれば自然と「共軍縮」ができる",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781907536,
      "updated": 1781907756
    },
    {
      "id": "6a35c0ad00000000003e7924",
      "text": "  日本に残された唯一の防衛的希望とも",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781907672,
      "updated": 1781907699
    },
    {
      "id": "6a35c01b00000000003e7921",
